channel.title: Home Teleport Error
channel.description:
Hi!
I have a problem. Every time I click the home teleport button it'll give me options on where to go so I tried changing it to this but now I have an error. Anyone Help? And I don't even won't the option I just want it to go straight to edgeville like any other normal teleport?
[IMG]http://img19.imageshack.us/img19/5508/errj.png[/img]

item.title: Home Teleport Error
item.dc:creator: @Svitkona Svitkona
item.description:
@Svitkona wrote:

clickingMost.java.
to get the case ID, click on the teleport then look in your run.bat window, you should see something like
playerName: case ID
search for that in clickingMost.java, and replace it with the above stuff. also add in the XXXX and YYYY co-ordinates. ALSO, backup before you edit it as to recover from any errors that might occur.
